<section class="mission">
  <div class="container mission-inner">
    <span class="mission-label" data-animate="fade-up">Our Purpose</span>
    <h2 class="mission-heading" data-animate="fade-up">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
    </h2>
    <div class="mission-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="mission-body-block" data-animate="fade-up">
      <p class="mission-body">
        Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia curae.
        Sed vehicula metus non justo facilisis, vel cursus libero efficitur. Nunc volutpat turpis
        quis nunc placerat, in fringilla sem venenatis.
      </p>
      <p class="mission-body">
        Curabitur ullamcorper facilisis tellus, ac malesuada sapien laoreet vel. Integer blandit
        semper ligula, eget elementum risus vestibulum non. Fusce suscipit orci vitae magna
        tempor rhoncus.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission {
    background: linear-gradient(
      168deg,
      var(--color-cream) 0%,
      var(--color-cream-light) 50%,
      var(--color-cream) 100%
    );
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl) 140px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .mission-inner {
    position: relative;
  }

  .mission-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
  }

  .mission-heading {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    line-height: 1.3;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .mission-accent {
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--color-orange);
    border-radius: 2px;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .mission-body-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .mission-body {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.7;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .mission-body-block {
      max-width: 100%;
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .mission-accent {
      margin-left: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
